text: Janel Meilani Parrish Long (born October 30, 1988) is an American actress and singer. She is best known for starring as Mona Vanderwaal in the mystery-drama franchise Pretty Little Liars (2010–2017, 2019) and as Margot Covey in the To All the Boys movie series (2018–present). ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Honolulu Category:Singers from Hawaii
